Third-party code included in this repository
-------------------------------------------

M. Saito Butterworth filter routines

The Butterworth filter coefficient routines in src/util.cpp are based on
filter routines by Masanori Saito:

  Saito, M. (1978), Automatic design of recursive digital filters,
  Butsuri-Tanko (Geophysical Exploration), 31, 112-135.

The routines were distributed as part of the WIN system, whose web page
states that WIN system source and manuals are free software under the
GNU General Public License. These routines are therefore treated as GPL
code in this repository.

